  "body": "Currently out gossip modules enforce chunk size on init, however the chunk size dynamically changes on bellatrix. While statically increasing the size isn't an issue for incoming payloads, its possible that we send out big chunks pre-bellatrix, however this is unlikely.\r\n\r\nA better fix would be dynamically impose the chunk size.\r\nContext: #3486",
